4 Days Ago Staff of the company, who had been in close contact with Dokpesi jnr., were also tested by the NCDC. The premises of DAAR Communications headquarters in Asokoro District, Abuja, was also fumigated and decontaminated by the Federal Capital Territory Health Authorities. 